desc_long									Academic Version									Click here for information about 001 Game Creator Academic.																						关于这款软件							Create games without limits001 Game Creator prides itself on offering users a diverse set of tools and features to create any type of game you can think of:Intuitive map editor featuring dynamic lighting, atmospheric weather effects and parallax backgrounds/foregrounds – with no restrictions on map layers.Fully customisable interfaces including (but not limited to): heads-up displays (HUD), loading screens, menus and dialogue boxes.Built-in graphics editor, allowing users to create their own sprites, tile-sets and items without needing to use external third-party solutions (of course you can still use external tools and import graphics if you prefer!)Flexible camera controls to set the stage and provide both 2D and 3D perspectives, with full camera scripting events and 3D model/animation importing.Sophisticated sprite customisation, with visible clothing and equipment changes in-game.Built-in artificial intelligence and actor routes, allowing users to create complex movement patterns and fine tune character behaviour.Support for up to 7.1 audio surround sound with built-in sound filters to control volume, pitch and speed variance.Powerful custom gestures for creating unique multi-finger triggers for mobile devices.Informative script and game debugging tools to step through events and monitor changes as they occur in real-time.Graphically Assisted Scripting001 Game Creator offers creators the ability to craft intuitive and imaginative games without any prior coding knowledge. This is especially beneficial to artists and designers who prefer a more hands-on and visualised approach or developers who don’t wish to spend hours bashing their head against a wall. Unlike traditional Event-Driven Programming applications, 001 Game Creator offers a huge set of built-in events, with the ability to also create custom events for specific tailor-made functionality just for your games.PC, HTML5 & mobile development all-in-one001 Game Creator allows developers to build their games for Windows PCs (.exe), HTML5 (.js/.html) and mobile devices (.apk) all-in-one! Unlike other similar engines, 001 Game Creator provides developers with the freedom to create their games for any and all platforms available without paying anything extra. Best of all, there are no additional license or revenue fees for selling your games - so if you’ve purchased a copy of 001 Game Creator you can sell your games without having to share the profits with us!The possibilities are endless001 Game Creator unlocks the doors to a wide range of possibilities. Make any game you can think of, including RPGs, shoot-‘em-ups, racing games, fighting games, simulation games, platformers, tower defense, card games, and even 3D games! If you can imagine it, you can create it with 001 Game Creator.						
